  "texts": [
    "Our online survey has several limitations.",
    "The use of convenience sampling through dementia organizations as gatekeepers, while practical, may introduce selection bias.",
    "This approach relies on participants who are actively engaged with these organizations and have access to the internet, potentially excluding a portion of the dementia population who are less active or lack online access.",
    "Additionally, sample sizes of 15 people with dementia and 14 supporters limit the statistical power of the study especially with regard to more subtle effects.",
    "It is also possible that in some cases both a PwD and their supporter filled in the questionnaire, leading to correlation between the samples."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}